3. Choose the photos you can see them using as a profile photo the most

One of the most important things in photography is composition. Composition is the way that you arrange the elements in your photo. It's important to think about the placement of your subject, the background, and the foreground. You want to create a photo that is visually pleasing and that tells a story.

Lighting is also important in photography. The way that you light your subject can make a big difference in the look of your photo. You want to make sure that your subject is well-lit and that there are no harsh shadows.
